Eswatini, on the other hand, approaches the match as underdogs. They will look to take advantage of the pressure on the Malian side and aim to cause an upset.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The stakes are high, and both teams know that every point matters.
Mali’s depth in talent suggests that they still have the upper hand against Eswatini.
The match against Eswatini presents the perfect opportunity for Mali to break this winless streak and revive their confidence as they continue their quest in the competition.
